  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-top-left-radius: 15px;border-top-right-radius: 15px;overflow: hidden;padding: 15px 0px 35px;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 97%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-radius: 9px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: #8db3e2 0px 3px 7px 0px;height: auto;padding: 24px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:97% !important;\">\n        <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family:PingFangSC-light;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2026年初，字节默默整了个新活——「随变」APP突然上线了。懂得都懂，这摆明是要在AI视频生成领域再造一个“抖音”，正面硬刚 OpenAI 的明星产品 Sora。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"text-align:center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9712962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 222px;height: 216px;box-sizing:border-box;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=306eece0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FDlA9ne3LKSp5NW1hGhmFYt7HYuicHqDcHjSddIOLsRPGXUpSUlC0GuTUf7qC0hn0fNjbNANZibzKY3CPhkLQwsMg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-family:PingFangSC-light;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为每天 5Ga 冲浪的抖音资深用户，本小A必然不能错过这新的玩法！</span></p>\n         <p nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-miniprogram class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_miniprogram_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"insertminiprogram\" data-miniprogram-path=\"pages/products/products?id=suibian&amp;time=26011901&amp;name=029weekgzh&amp;article=suibian\" data-miniprogram-nickname=\"模力工场\" data-miniprogram-avatar=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/Y8icB3ibIaic29vnNVPicaqXP8s9Kib4EUoU26V7yVpQGT9gpvjpIu5YxyWpS9h9EHBNhRTalCBB6ALyOBEia89jc4Rg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;wxfrom=200\" data-miniprogram-title=\"随变\" data-miniprogram-imageurl=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_jpg/DlA9ne3LKSp5NW1hGhmFYt7HYuicHqDcHIRFaKjtOuribibkqwKvLvQHM0ZqM07wFlzgIibvXD5ydHk3kA9P66M2zw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-miniprogram-type=\"card\" data-miniprogram-servicetype=\"0\" data-miniprogram-appid=\"wx911b23c54b795c5f\" data-miniprogram-imageurlback=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FDlA9ne3LKSp5NW1hGhmFYt7HYuicHqDcHpX1ib5JXNZRuPoGFp91xNJ9Xkdy9JGzdNaDiaCX60NRpeZ9ciaviaSrAgQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\" data-miniprogram-cropperinfo=\"%7B%22c%22%3A%7B%22x%22%3A0%2C%22y%22%3A38%2C%22x2%22%3A245%2C%22y2%22%3A234%2C%22w%22%3A245%2C%22h%22%3A196%7D%7D\"></mp-common-miniprogram></p>\n         <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">打开</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">「随变」第一眼：好家伙，界面完全是抖音那味儿——只是顶上只剩“关注”和“推荐”俩标签。</span></span></span></strong></p>\n         <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">仔细一看，抖音那些花里胡哨的滤镜全被阉割掉了，只留下两个入口：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\">创作</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">和</span><strong><span leaf=\"\">合拍</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">不同于Sora的文生视频形式，在使用</span><strong><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-top-left-radius: 15px;border-top-right-radius: 15px;overflow: hidden;padding: 15px 0px 35px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;display: inline-block;width: 97%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-radius: 9px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(255, 201, 140) 0px 3px 7px 0px;height: auto;padding: 24px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">「随变」之前</span></span></span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，你需要给自己捏一个 AI 形象——作为”你在随变里的数字分身”。</span></p>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0% -10px;justify-content: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"margin: 0px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n           <div style=\"color: #999999;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: #3b6fb3;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: #cdcdcd;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">左右滑动查看更多</span></span></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\">\n         <div style=\"overflow: hidden;width: 300%;max-width: 300% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n          <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 33.3333%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:33.3333% !important;\">\n           <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 94%;height: auto;box-sizing:border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.9351851851851851\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f9a76128&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FDlA9ne3LKSp5NW1hGhmFYt7HYuicHqDcHu3CAENeziaJicZEXmz4ibB1PIibBlEnibc02I1ibGOWDCAgy9F6QiasBHTibhw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 33.3333%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:33.3333% !important;\">\n           <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 94%;height: auto;box-sizing:border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.051851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ee6b66c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FDlA9ne3LKSp5NW1hGhmFYt7HYuicHqDcHBu7DZJawILPibLibUSOHMCB3wUAibap6zwmSZwXGGUUP22odsHAO03olw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 33.3333%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:33.3333% !important;\">\n           <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n            <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;width: 94%;height: auto;box-sizing:border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.049074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" width=\"100%\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a6483d1c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FDlA9ne3LKSp5NW1hGhmFYt7HYuicHqDcHBsF35m3Rfj5u8LUa4iaZ31XIylbq9RY1cEt2icI6OM9925ZG66jPPdOA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">点开创作功能，它提供了图片、动图和视频三种格式。仔细一看，里面集合的模板挺眼熟的——像蓝调摄影滤镜、渐变色光影这些热门滤镜，还有粘土风、治愈日漫风这类在小某书上很火的风格，甚至“变身”“帅哥来抱我”这类视频模板也都有。感觉上，它和「剪映」在功能和模板上确实有不少重叠。</span></p>\n        <p nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: baseline;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100000670\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2c1c0e05&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FDlA9ne3LKSp5NW1hGhmFYt7HYuicHqDcHMu9MLCBG7lCjF3Sx12by6E7NoqtQo6ygxjJs06ERK5bAYOttUw1H4g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        <p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;display: inline-block;width: 97%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-radius: 9px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(255, 201, 140) 0px 3px 7px 0px;height: auto;padding: 24px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（图源随变AI生成）</span></span></span></p>\n        <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;margin-top:0px !important;margin-bottom:16px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">合拍这一点做得挺有意思的。只要我捏出专属形象，就能和一些经典角色——比如企鹅或蒙娜丽莎——搭在一起，组个CP，玩出点互动感。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:16px;font-family:quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:0px !important;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">它还提供了一些预设的提示词模板，像是过年相关的“包饺砸🧨”，或者“企鹅跳舞”这种简单场景。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin-bottom:-13px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n        <span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">不过实测下来，确实还是有点小遗憾。目前它生成视频的方式比较固定，只能采用“已有模板图+预设提示词”的组合来做图生视频，还不支持完全自由文本生成，也不能混合多种元素进行更个性化的创作。</span></span>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 35px;color: #3b6fb3;text-align: right;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 场景测试</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 97%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-radius: 9px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: #8db3e2 0px 3px 7px 0px;height: auto;padding: 24px;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:97% !important;\">\n      <div style=\"line-height:1.75;font-family:PingFangSC-light;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">除此之外，「模力工场测评团」还拉来了 Sora 等国内外热门的 AI 视频工具，给「随变」来了场硬核的“横向测评”。本次测评将围绕两个场景、三个核心维度展开，测试</span><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;display: inline-block;width: 97%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-radius: 9px;overflow: hidden;box-shadow: rgb(255, 201, 140) 0px 3px 7px 0px;height: auto;padding: 24px;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height: 1.75;font-family: PingFangSC-light;box-sizing: border-box;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\">「随变」的 AI 生视频能力</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"caret-color:#000000;padding:0px;margin:0px;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">场景一：动作合理性与流畅度</span></p>\n       <p style=\"caret-color:#000000;padding:0px;margin:0px;white-space:normal;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"caret-color:#000000;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">prompt：</span></span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 8px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertic